  <brief_title>Investigation of the Steady State Pharmacokinetics of Sirolimus, Mycophenolat Mofetil and Fluvastatin After Renal Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Investigation of the Steady State Pharmacokinetics of Sirolimus, Mycophenolat Mofetil and Fluvastatin After Renal Transplantation</official_title>
