  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate in renal transplant recipients the potential drug intreaction between
      Sirolimus, Mycophenolt Mofetil and Fluvastatin

      All patient enrolled in this PKI-Study had no changes in the therapy before or because of the
      study. Only patients without changes more than 4 weeks before startin the study were included
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
